{
  "video_id": "I1cGiNnJZgU",
  "title": "Why civilians suffer more once a war is over | Margaret Bourdeaux",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12798.0,
      "end_time": 15900.0,
      "text": "So have you ever wondered what it would be like"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15924.0,
      "end_time": 18497.0,
      "text": "to live in a place with no rules?"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19653.0,
      "end_time": 20804.0,
      "text": "That sounds pretty cool."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20828.0,
      "end_time": 21866.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21890.0,
      "end_time": 23527.0,
      "text": "You wake up one morning, however,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 23551.0,
      "end_time": 26310.0,
      "text": "and you discover that the reason there are no rules"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 26550.0,
      "end_time": 29416.0,
      "text": "is because there&#39;s no government, and there are no laws."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 29440.0,
      "end_time": 33507.0,
      "text": "In fact, all social institutions have disappeared."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34738.0,
      "end_time": 36710.0,
      "text": "So there&#39;s no schools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36950.0,
      "end_time": 37260.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s no hospitals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 37285.0,
      "end_time": 38593.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s no police,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 38617.0,
      "end_time": 39952.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s no banks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 39976.0,
      "end_time": 42530.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s no athletic clubs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 42554.0,
      "end_time": 44570.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s no utilities."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 44704.0,
      "end_time": 47896.0,
      "text": "Well, I know a little bit about what this is like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 47920.0,
      "end_time": 50769.0,
      "text": "because when I was a medical student in 1999,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 50793.0,
      "end_time": 55278.0,
      "text": "I worked in a refugee camp in the Balkans during the Kosovo War."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 56829.0,
      "end_time": 57979.0,
      "text": "When the war was over,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 58300.0,
      "end_time": 61610.0,
      "text": "I got permission -- unbelievably -- from my medical school"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 61850.0,
      "end_time": 62236.0,
      "text": "to take some time off"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 62260.0,
      "end_time": 66431.0,
      "text": "and follow some of the families that I had befriended in the camp"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 66455.0,
      "end_time": 68878.0,
      "text": "back to their village in Kosovo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 68902.0,
      "end_time": 74269.0,
      "text": "and understand how they navigated life in this postwar setting."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 76331.0,
      "end_time": 79551.0,
      "text": "Postwar Kosovo was a very interesting place"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 79575.0,
      "end_time": 82744.0,
      "text": "because NATO troops were there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 82768.0,
      "end_time": 86404.0,
      "text": "mostly to make sure the war didn&#39;t break out again."
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 86428.0,
      "end_time": 89920.0,
      "text": "But other than that, it was actually a lawless place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 89945.0,
      "end_time": 93210.0,
      "text": "and almost every social institution, both public and private,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 93234.0,
      "end_time": 94509.0,
      "text": "had been destroyed."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 95439.0,
      "end_time": 99327.0,
      "text": "So I can tell you"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 99352.0,
      "end_time": 103867.0,
      "text": "that when you go into one of these situations and settings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 103891.0,
      "end_time": 107698.0,
      "text": "it is absolutely thrilling ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 107722.0,
      "end_time": 109740.0,
      "text": "for about 30 minutes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 109980.0,
      "end_time": 113770.0,
      "text": "because that&#39;s about how long it takes before you run into a situation"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 113794.0,
      "end_time": 118337.0,
      "text": "where you realize how incredibly vulnerable you are."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 119540.0,
      "end_time": 123307.0,
      "text": "For me, that moment came when I had to cross the first checkpoint,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 123331.0,
      "end_time": 125124.0,
      "text": "and I realized as I drove up"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 125148.0,
      "end_time": 129246.0,
      "text": "that I would be negotiating passage through this checkpoint"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 129270.00000000001,
      "end_time": 131484.0,
      "text": "with a heavily armed individual"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 131508.0,
      "end_time": 134894.0,
      "text": "who, if he decided to shoot me right then and there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 134918.0,
      "end_time": 137248.0,
      "text": "actually wouldn&#39;t be doing anything illegal."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 138811.0,
      "end_time": 143674.0,
      "text": "But the sense of vulnerability that I had was absolutely nothing"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 143698.0,
      "end_time": 147596.0,
      "text": "in comparison to the vulnerability of the families that I got to know"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 147620.0,
      "end_time": 149280.0,
      "text": "over that year."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 149304.0,
      "end_time": 154417.0,
      "text": "You see, life in a society where there are no social institutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 154441.0,
      "end_time": 157885.0,
      "text": "is riddled with danger and uncertainty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 157909.0,
      "end_time": 161283.0,
      "text": "and simple questions like, \"What are we going to eat tonight?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 162245.0,
      "end_time": 164926.0,
      "text": "are very complicated to answer."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 166559.0,
      "end_time": 170909.0,
      "text": "Questions about security, when you don&#39;t have any security systems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 170933.0,
      "end_time": 172351.0,
      "text": "are terrifying."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 172375.0,
      "end_time": 175138.0,
      "text": "Is that altercation I had with the neighbor down the block"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 175162.0,
      "end_time": 177976.0,
      "text": "going to turn into a violent episode that will end my life"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 178000.0,
      "end_time": 179237.0,
      "text": "or my family&#39;s life?"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 179843.0,
      "end_time": 182768.0,
      "text": "Health concerns when there is no health system"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 182793.0,
      "end_time": 184333.0,
      "text": "are also terrifying."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 185114.0,
      "end_time": 188732.0,
      "text": "I listened as many families had to sort through questions like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 188756.0,
      "end_time": 191629.0,
      "text": "\"My infant has a fever. What am I going to do?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 192243.0,
      "end_time": 195923.0,
      "text": "\"My sister, who is pregnant, is bleeding. What should I do?"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 195947.0,
      "end_time": 197121.0,
      "text": "Who should I turn to?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 197145.0,
      "end_time": 199275.0,
      "text": "\"Where are the doctors, where are the nurses?"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 199299.0,
      "end_time": 202600.0,
      "text": "If I could find one, are they trustworthy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 202840.0,
      "end_time": 204817.0,
      "text": "How will I pay them? In what currency will I pay them?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 204841.0,
      "end_time": 207635.0,
      "text": "\"If I need medications, where will I find them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 208664.0,
      "end_time": 211559.0,
      "text": "If I take those medications, are they actually counterfeits?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 211583.0,
      "end_time": 213820.0,
      "text": "And on and on."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 214765.0,
      "end_time": 217137.0,
      "text": "So for life in these settings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 217161.0,
      "end_time": 221641.0,
      "text": "the dominant theme, the dominant feature of life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 221665.0,
      "end_time": 225608.0,
      "text": "is the incredible vulnerability that people have to manage"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 225632.0,
      "end_time": 227181.0,
      "text": "day in and day out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 227205.0,
      "end_time": 230390.0,
      "text": "because of the lack of social systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 230630.0,
      "end_time": 231298.0,
      "text": "And it actually turns out"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 231323.0,
      "end_time": 235350.0,
      "text": "that this feature of life is incredibly difficult to explain"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 235374.0,
      "end_time": 238349.0,
      "text": "and be understood by people who are living outside of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 239410.0,
      "end_time": 243677.0,
      "text": "I discovered this when I left Kosovo."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 243701.0,
      "end_time": 246906.0,
      "text": "I came back to Boston, I became a physician,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 246930.0,
      "end_time": 250941.0,
      "text": "I became a global public health policy researcher."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 250965.0,
      "end_time": 252755.0,
      "text": "I joined the Harvard Medical School"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 252779.0,
      "end_time": 255621.0,
      "text": "and Brigham and Women&#39;s Hospital Division of Global Health."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 255645.0,
      "end_time": 256879.0,
      "text": "And I, as a researcher,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 256903.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259557.00000000003,
      "text": "really wanted to get started on this problem right away."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 259581.00000000003,
      "end_time": 263149.0,
      "text": "I was like, \"How do we reduce the crushing vulnerability"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 263173.0,
      "end_time": 266944.0,
      "text": "of people living in these types of fragile settings?"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 266968.0,
      "end_time": 269437.0,
      "text": "Is there any way we can start to think about"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 269461.0,
      "end_time": 272166.0,
      "text": "how to protect and quickly recover"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 272190.0,
      "end_time": 274999.0,
      "text": "the institutions that are critical to survival,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 275230.0,
      "end_time": 276536.0,
      "text": "like the health system?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 276560.0,
      "end_time": 279881.0,
      "text": "And I have to say, I had amazing colleagues."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 280402.0,
      "end_time": 282288.0,
      "text": "But one interesting thing about it was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 282312.0,
      "end_time": 284796.0,
      "text": "this was sort of an unusual question for them."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 284820.0,
      "end_time": 287129.0,
      "text": "They were kind of like, \"Oh, if you work in war,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 287153.0,
      "end_time": 289402.0,
      "text": "doesn&#39;t that mean you work on refugee camps,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 289426.0,
      "end_time": 291858.0,
      "text": "and you work on documenting mass atrocities?\" --"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 291882.0,
      "end_time": 294482.0,
      "text": "which is, by the way, very, very, very important."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 295297.0,
      "end_time": 300451.0,
      "text": "So it took me a while to explain why I was so passionate about this issue,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 300475.0,
      "end_time": 302166.0,
      "text": "until about six years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 302190.0,
      "end_time": 304255.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s when this landmark study"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 304279.0,
      "end_time": 308388.0,
      "text": "that looked at and described the public health consequences of war"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 308412.0,
      "end_time": 309753.0,
      "text": "was published."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 309778.0,
      "end_time": 314715.0,
      "text": "They came to an incredible, provocative conclusion."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 315671.0,
      "end_time": 318320.0,
      "text": "These researchers concluded"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 318344.0,
      "end_time": 321818.0,
      "text": "that the vast majority of death and disability from war"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 321842.0,
      "end_time": 324474.0,
      "text": "happens after the cessation of conflict."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 324499.0,
      "end_time": 329537.0,
      "text": "So the most dangerous time to be a person living in a conflict-affected state"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 329561.0,
      "end_time": 331604.0,
      "text": "is after the cessation of hostilities;"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 331628.0,
      "end_time": 333628.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s after the peace deal has been signed."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 333653.0,
      "end_time": 336214.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s when that political solution has been achieved."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 336238.0,
      "end_time": 339772.0,
      "text": "That seems so puzzling, but of course it&#39;s not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 339796.0,
      "end_time": 345601.0,
      "text": "because war kills people by robbing them of their clinics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 345625.0,
      "end_time": 346802.0,
      "text": "of their hospitals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 346826.0,
      "end_time": 348690.0,
      "text": "of their supply chains."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 348714.0,
      "end_time": 352305.0,
      "text": "Their doctors are targeted, are killed; they&#39;re on the run."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 352329.0,
      "end_time": 356248.0,
      "text": "And more invisible and yet more deadly is the destruction"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 356272.0,
      "end_time": 359808.0,
      "text": "of the health governance institutions and their finances."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 360938.0,
      "end_time": 364176.0,
      "text": "So this is really not surprising at all to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 365610.0,
      "end_time": 368160.0,
      "text": "But what is surprising and somewhat dismaying,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 368184.0,
      "end_time": 372158.0,
      "text": "is how little impact this insight has had,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 372182.0,
      "end_time": 375766.0,
      "text": "in terms of how we think about human suffering and war."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 376499.0,
      "end_time": 378206.0,
      "text": "Let me give you a couple examples."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 378926.0,
      "end_time": 380837.0,
      "text": "Last year, you may remember,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 380861.0,
      "end_time": 384986.0,
      "text": "Ebola hit the West African country of Liberia."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 385981.0,
      "end_time": 389849.0,
      "text": "There was a lot of reporting about this group, Doctors Without Borders,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 389873.0,
      "end_time": 392771.0,
      "text": "sounding the alarm and calling for aid and assistance."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 393322.0,
      "end_time": 397184.0,
      "text": "But not a lot of that reporting answered the question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 397208.0,
      "end_time": 399760.0,
      "text": "Why is Doctors Without Borders even in Liberia?"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 399784.0,
      "end_time": 402460.0,
      "text": "Doctors Without Borders is an amazing organization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 402484.0,
      "end_time": 406899.0,
      "text": "dedicated and designed to provide emergency care in war zones."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 407461.0,
      "end_time": 410278.0,
      "text": "Liberia&#39;s civil war had ended in 2003 --"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 410302.0,
      "end_time": 413139.0,
      "text": "that was 11 years before Ebola even struck."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 414452.0,
      "end_time": 416172.0,
      "text": "When Ebola struck Liberia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 416196.0,
      "end_time": 419823.0,
      "text": "there were less than 50 doctors in the entire country"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 419847.0,
      "end_time": 421709.0,
      "text": "of 4.5 million people."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 422529.0,
      "end_time": 424713.0,
      "text": "Doctors Without Borders is in Liberia"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 424737.0,
      "end_time": 428118.0,
      "text": "because Liberia still doesn&#39;t really have a functioning health system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 428142.0,
      "end_time": 429808.0,
      "text": "11 years later."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 429833.0,
      "end_time": 433145.0,
      "text": "When the earthquake hit Haiti in 2010,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 433169.0,
      "end_time": 436702.0,
      "text": "the outpouring of international aid was phenomenal."
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 436726.0,
      "end_time": 440397.0,
      "text": "But did you know that only two percent of that funding"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 440421.0,
      "end_time": 443263.0,
      "text": "went to rebuild Haitian public institutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 443287.0,
      "end_time": 445460.0,
      "text": "including its health sector?"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 445697.0,
      "end_time": 447114.0,
      "text": "From that perspective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 447138.0,
      "end_time": 450513.0,
      "text": "Haitians continue to die from the earthquake even today."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 451663.0,
      "end_time": 453740.0,
      "text": "I recently met this gentleman."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 453764.0,
      "end_time": 455842.0,
      "text": "This is Dr. Nezar Ismet."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 455866.0,
      "end_time": 459702.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s the Minister of Health in the northern autonomous region of Iraq,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 459726.0,
      "end_time": 461157.0,
      "text": "in Kurdistan."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 461181.0,
      "end_time": 465630.0,
      "text": "Here he is announcing that in the last nine months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 465870.0,
      "end_time": 469128.0,
      "text": "his country, his region, has increased from four million people"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 469153.0,
      "end_time": 470685.0,
      "text": "to five million people."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 470709.0,
      "end_time": 472577.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s a 25 percent increase."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 472601.0,
      "end_time": 476467.0,
      "text": "Thousands of these new arrivals have experienced incredible trauma."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 476979.0,
      "end_time": 481174.0,
      "text": "His doctors are working 16-hour days without pay."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 482867.0,
      "end_time": 485690.0,
      "text": "His budget has not increased by 25 percent;"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 485714.0,
      "end_time": 488109.0,
      "text": "it has decreased by 20 percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 488133.0,
      "end_time": 492774.0,
      "text": "as funding has flowed to security concerns and to short-term relief efforts."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 493569.0,
      "end_time": 495173.0,
      "text": "When his health sector fails --"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 495197.0,
      "end_time": 497610.0,
      "text": "and if history is any guide, it will --"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 497634.0,
      "end_time": 499680.0,
      "text": "how do you think that&#39;s going to influence"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 499704.0,
      "end_time": 502936.0,
      "text": "the decision making of the five million people in his region"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 502960.0,
      "end_time": 505779.0,
      "text": "as they think about whether they should flee"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 505803.0,
      "end_time": 508294.0,
      "text": "that type of vulnerable living situation?"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 509550.0,
      "end_time": 512484.0,
      "text": "So as you can see, this is a frustrating topic for me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 512508.00000000006,
      "end_time": 514100.00000000006,
      "text": "and I really try to understand:"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 514340.00000000006,
      "end_time": 517558.00000000006,
      "text": "Why the reluctance to protect and support"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 517582.0,
      "end_time": 521217.0,
      "text": "indigenous health systems and security systems?"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 521241.0,
      "end_time": 523861.0,
      "text": "I usually tier two concerns, two arguments."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 524747.0,
      "end_time": 526934.0,
      "text": "The first concern is about corruption,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 526958.0,
      "end_time": 529677.0,
      "text": "and the concern that people in these settings are corrupt"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 529701.0,
      "end_time": 531446.0,
      "text": "and they are untrustworthy."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 532760.0,
      "end_time": 535137.0,
      "text": "And I will admit that I have met unsavory characters"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 535161.0,
      "end_time": 537516.0,
      "text": "working in health sectors in these situations."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 537541.0,
      "end_time": 541241.0,
      "text": "But I will tell you that the opposite is absolutely true"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 541265.0,
      "end_time": 543295.0,
      "text": "in every case I have worked on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 543319.0,
      "end_time": 547132.0,
      "text": "from Afghanistan to Libya, to Kosovo, to Haiti, to Liberia --"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 547156.0,
      "end_time": 549255.0,
      "text": "I have met inspiring people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 549279.0,
      "end_time": 551774.0,
      "text": "who, when the chips were down for their country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 551798.0,
      "end_time": 555107.0,
      "text": "they risked everything to save their health institutions."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 555131.0,
      "end_time": 558478.0,
      "text": "The trick for the outsider who wants to help"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 558503.0,
      "end_time": 561407.0,
      "text": "is identifying who those individuals are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 561431.0,
      "end_time": 563739.0,
      "text": "and building a pathway for them to lead."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 563763.0,
      "end_time": 566947.0,
      "text": "That is exactly what happened in Afghanistan."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 567534.0,
      "end_time": 570863.0,
      "text": "One of the unsung and untold success stories"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 570887.0,
      "end_time": 573805.0,
      "text": "of our nation-building effort in Afghanistan"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 573829.0,
      "end_time": 577324.0,
      "text": "involved the World Bank in 2002 investing heavily"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 577349.0,
      "end_time": 582484.0,
      "text": "in identifying, training and promoting Afghani health sector leaders."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 583869.0,
      "end_time": 587722.0,
      "text": "These health sector leaders have pulled off an incredible feat"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 587746.0,
      "end_time": 589117.0,
      "text": "in Afghanistan."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 589142.0,
      "end_time": 593890.0,
      "text": "They have aggressively increased access to health care"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 593113.0,
      "end_time": 595129.0,
      "text": "for the majority of the population."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 595153.0,
      "end_time": 597357.0,
      "text": "They are rapidly improving the health status"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 597381.0,
      "end_time": 598651.0,
      "text": "of the Afghan population,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 598676.0,
      "end_time": 600662.0,
      "text": "which used to be the worst in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 601765.0,
      "end_time": 604587.0,
      "text": "In fact, the Afghan Ministry of Health does things"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 604611.0,
      "end_time": 606307.0,
      "text": "that I wish we would do in America."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 606331.0,
      "end_time": 608703.0,
      "text": "They use things like data to make policy."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 608727.0,
      "end_time": 609911.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s incredible."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 609936.0,
      "end_time": 612328.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 612352.0,
      "end_time": 614281.0,
      "text": "The other concern I hear a lot about is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 614305.0,
      "end_time": 616906.0,
      "text": "\"We just can&#39;t afford it, we just don&#39;t have the money."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 616931.0,
      "end_time": 618286.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just unsustainable.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 619239.0,
      "end_time": 621972.0,
      "text": "I would submit to you that the current situation"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 621996.0,
      "end_time": 623731.0,
      "text": "and the current system we have"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 623755.0,
      "end_time": 627793.0,
      "text": "is the most expensive, inefficient system we could possibly conceive of."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 627817.0,
      "end_time": 631195.0,
      "text": "The current situation is that when governments like the US --"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 631219.0,
      "end_time": 633283.0,
      "text": "or, let&#39;s say, the collection of governments"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 633307.0,
      "end_time": 635181.0,
      "text": "that make up the European Commission --"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 635205.0,
      "end_time": 637854.0,
      "text": "every year, they spend 15 billion dollars"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 637878.0,
      "end_time": 641884.0,
      "text": "on just humanitarian and emergency and disaster relief worldwide."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 641908.0,
      "end_time": 645229.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s nothing about foreign aid, that&#39;s just disaster relief."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 645895.0,
      "end_time": 650939.0,
      "text": "Ninety-five percent of it goes to international relief agencies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 650964.0,
      "end_time": 655301.0,
      "text": "that then have to import resources into these areas,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 655325.0,
      "end_time": 659714.0,
      "text": "and knit together some type of temporary health system, let&#39;s say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 659738.0,
      "end_time": 663307.0,
      "text": "which they then dismantle and send away when they run out of money."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 664100.0,
      "end_time": 667930.0,
      "text": "So our job, it turns out, is very clear."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 669100.0,
      "end_time": 673776.0,
      "text": "We, as the global health community policy experts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 673800.0,
      "end_time": 679344.0,
      "text": "our first job is to become experts in how to monitor"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 679369.0,
      "end_time": 681816.0,
      "text": "the strengths and vulnerabilities of health systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 681840.0,
      "end_time": 684407.0,
      "text": "in threatened situations."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 684431.0,
      "end_time": 686441.0,
      "text": "And that&#39;s when we see doctors fleeing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 686465.0,
      "end_time": 688402.0,
      "text": "when we see health resources drying up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 688426.0,
      "end_time": 690861.0,
      "text": "when we see institutions crumbling --"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 690885.0,
      "end_time": 692498.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s the emergency."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 692522.0,
      "end_time": 695632.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s when we need to sound the alarm and wave our arms."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 695656.0,
      "end_time": 697500.0,
      "text": "OK?"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 697740.0,
      "end_time": 698224.0,
      "text": "Not now."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 698249.0,
      "end_time": 702161.0,
      "text": "Everyone can see that&#39;s an emergency, they don&#39;t need us to tell them that."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 702942.0,
      "end_time": 704881.0,
      "text": "Number two:"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 704905.0,
      "end_time": 708242.0,
      "text": "places like where I work at Harvard need to take their cue"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 708266.0,
      "end_time": 710464.0,
      "text": "from the World Bank experience in Afghanistan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 710488.0,
      "end_time": 712145.0,
      "text": "and we need to -- and we will --"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 712169.0,
      "end_time": 717432.0,
      "text": "build robust platforms to support health sector leaders like these."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 718291.0,
      "end_time": 719993.0,
      "text": "These people risk their lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 720170.0,
      "end_time": 723729.0,
      "text": "I think we can match their courage with some support."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 724245.0,
      "end_time": 725399.0,
      "text": "Number three:"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 725423.0,
      "end_time": 728100.0,
      "text": "we need to reach out and make new partnerships."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 728250.0,
      "end_time": 729899.0,
      "text": "At our global health center,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 729923.0,
      "end_time": 733935.0,
      "text": "we have launched a new initiative with NATO and other security policy makers"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 733959.0,
      "end_time": 739324.0,
      "text": "to explore with them what they can do to protect health system institutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 739349.0,
      "end_time": 741640.0,
      "text": "during deployments."
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 741880.0,
      "end_time": 742627.0,
      "text": "We want them to see"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 742652.0,
      "end_time": 747352.0,
      "text": "that protecting health systems and other critical social institutions"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 747376.0,
      "end_time": 749819.0,
      "text": "is an integral part of their mission."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 749843.0,
      "end_time": 752979.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s not just about avoiding collateral damage;"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 753400.0,
      "end_time": 754809.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s about winning the peace."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 756545.0,
      "end_time": 760127.0,
      "text": "But the most important partner we need to engage is you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 760152.0,
      "end_time": 763584.0,
      "text": "the American public, and indeed, the world public."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 763608.0,
      "end_time": 769304.0,
      "text": "Because unless you understand the value of social institutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 769328.0,
      "end_time": 771839.0,
      "text": "like health systems in these fragile settings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 772886.0,
      "end_time": 775134.0,
      "text": "you won&#39;t support efforts to save them."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 775158.0,
      "end_time": 777556.0,
      "text": "You won&#39;t click on that article"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 777580.0,
      "end_time": 782546.0,
      "text": "that talks about \"Hey, all those doctors are on the run in country X."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 782570.0,
      "end_time": 784987.0,
      "text": "I wonder what that means."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 785110.0,
      "end_time": 786863.0,
      "text": "I wonder what that means"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 786887.0,
      "end_time": 790839.0,
      "text": "for that health system&#39;s ability to, let&#39;s say, detect influenza.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 791673.0,
      "end_time": 795500.0,
      "text": "\"Hmm, it&#39;s probably not good.\" That&#39;s what I&#39;d tell you."
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 795590.0,
      "end_time": 796754.0,
      "text": "Up on the screen,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 796778.0,
      "end_time": 803580.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve put up my three favorite American institution defenders and builders."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 803666.0,
      "end_time": 806551.0,
      "text": "Over here is George C. Marshall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 806575.0,
      "end_time": 809404.0,
      "text": "he was the guy that proposed the Marshall Plan"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 809428.0,
      "end_time": 813619.0,
      "text": "to save all of Europe&#39;s economic institutions after World War II."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 814119.0,
      "end_time": 816472.0,
      "text": "And this Eleanor Roosevelt."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 816496.0,
      "end_time": 819641.0,
      "text": "Her work on human rights really serves as the foundation"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 819666.0,
      "end_time": 822694.0,
      "text": "for all of our international human rights organizations."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 823150.0,
      "end_time": 825189.0,
      "text": "Then my big favorite is Ben Franklin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 825214.0,
      "end_time": 828422.0,
      "text": "who did many things in terms of creating institutions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 828446.0,
      "end_time": 831213.0,
      "text": "but was the midwife of our constitution."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 832402.0,
      "end_time": 834126.0,
      "text": "And I would say to you"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 834150.0,
      "end_time": 837903.0,
      "text": "that these are folks who, when our country was threatened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 837927.0,
      "end_time": 839934.0,
      "text": "or our world was threatened,"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 839958.0,
      "end_time": 841261.0,
      "text": "they didn&#39;t retreat."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 841285.0,
      "end_time": 843626.0,
      "text": "They didn&#39;t talk about building walls."
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
